{"tid":794700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"CITY仔嚟緊升YR4 想做考機師 求路過巴絲俾D意見","createTime":"2018-08-26T12:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T14:13:12.000Z","uid":181853,"like":67,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d4201814a715f9312bf36f7e77abcccf4be32a25","tid":794700,"uid":181853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，依個我嘅處女post，主要係想問下考機師嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n細佬今年升yr4，major如username所見高登神科CityU NRE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n我知核工神科真係笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但係真心向各位巴絲求教。<br />\n今年summer有個friend推介玩咗HKIAA個Aviation Engineering Day Camp之後落咗坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n原本諗住一grad就去考入境仔做一世算數，<br />\n玩完依個camp突然覺得唔想咁就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，難得搵到一樣自己鐘意嘅嘢，所以想膽粗粗想去考飛行員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n我對於航空業基本上係零認知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，飛機點飛起都係啱啱依個camp先識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其他campmate全部有底，淨係齋睇機身、咩引擎已經知係咩型號，超級佩服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n所以玩完之後開始睇BAK慢慢學，宜家日日摺CITY拉把慢慢撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n我知做飛行員英文要好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但細佬英文差，DSE得Level 3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以睇BAK都要逐隻逐字查，所以嚟緊開學都會落CITY嗰個ELC同多D鬼仔鬼妹開CHAT GROUP仲有上D英文COURSES，順便練埋同鬼佬傾計嘅膽量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n我知條路好長好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但我好想去做一D我覺得值得堅持嘅嘢，就算到最尾考唔到，走去做飛機工程，我都甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為我起碼有試過。如果連試都唔試嘅話，根本冇資格去話自己係人。<br />\n我係遲起步，對於嗰D中學甚至再細D就已經接觸嘅人好「鄧」佢地開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為已經好早搵到自己興趣去奮發圖強，而我希望GRAD完之後一年裏面可以玩到HKYAA/CATHAY DRAGOON嗰個PROGRAM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，就算考唔到都可以繼續自修aviation嘅書，做到想做嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n知道考國泰應該都入唔到，自知冇咁嘅能力，但如果係中國嗰D航空公司有冇得諗, e.g. 華航?<br />\n希望睇到依個post嘅人，不論係支持、反對，或者係同樣處境嘅人，都可以放低你嘅comment，俾細佬參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：樓主加油<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：樓豬好天真，放棄吧喇。"},{"pid":"e0af40d8cce25e1c7756f88f0d3b5a4a53405548","tid":794700,"uid":93640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:45:07.000Z","msg":"練英文: youtube Rachel's English<br />\n<br />\nbtw你呢科真係好伏?"},{"pid":"fb09b5b5a4958f7e36342dae82550ee77344767f","tid":794700,"uid":24764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"真係識人考到 但條友本身英文好撚勁"},{"pid":"7234ceaeb86c11c7bad9cc3cdad4c52d78a5de65","tid":794700,"uid":197852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"唔好害人啦"},{"pid":"5a07447409b4c98bde45e5a17637195f3bfdca96","tid":794700,"uid":36296,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"Eng level3 <br />\n唔係話睇死你 英文係要浸架 你以為同鬼講兩句就會進步？ 會唔會太樂觀<br />\n<br />\n當你每講一句都要係個腦入邊 由中文轉英文講既話<br />\n我都覺得你唔好去做算啦"},{"pid":"1cfac2871b9c724aa4e6f49b4bf984668ea0aa6c","tid":794700,"uid":39393,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n係連登一定會好多人笑你<br />\n唔好放棄<br />\n<br />\n利申 city仔 都係lib睇bak"},{"pid":"ed6eddf3591207f0f7e7824bfdefacf8242c9fdd","tid":794700,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:52:31.000Z","msg":"十卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4d281e9422d7479afb94f8388e8e663e964ba6","tid":794700,"uid":50767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"飛乜撚野行員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69adcd59575c3d5de6b92ac6908b1369b5c00564","tid":794700,"uid":78165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:53:15.000Z","msg":"有冇錢，識唔識人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbc77b0de9a54fd14139ff1574c9604095d87ef","tid":794700,"uid":93206,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"其實英文3真係死穴 識人去考成組有kongu 有外國回流乜乜乜 最後無一個過到..."},{"pid":"baef204887bd2f45b18ce1c0a854397b13d409f7","tid":794700,"uid":23499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"識人英文好撚差但做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1def839a96f5c61a8baef9754311a9254a551c23","tid":794700,"uid":23499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:57:19.000Z","msg":"唔好聽人鳩up 啦，真係有心就睇多啲書build up 個passion 唔係人地問你點解想做都講唔到"},{"pid":"114def48799aa540da8a5a2dee5d7e03018ca97a","tid":794700,"uid":181853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0af40d8cce25e1c7756f88f0d3b5a4a53405548","tid":794700,"uid":93640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:45:07.000Z","msg":"練英文: youtube Rachel's English<br />\n<br />\nbtw你呢科真係好伏?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"多謝你意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n答翻你問題：有得揀唔好揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c90429822c4f1f6897f03a6b017c201bd8e1d08","tid":794700,"uid":152283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"做人冇夢想，同鹹魚有何異<br />\n巴打加油！"},{"pid":"927fb537c1a725693a264d4d0ef2f9eacc849b34","tid":794700,"uid":36296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a07447409b4c98bde45e5a17637195f3bfdca96","tid":794700,"uid":36296,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"Eng level3 <br />\n唔係話睇死你 英文係要浸架 你以為同鬼講兩句就會進步？ 會唔會太樂觀<br />\n<br />\n當你每講一句都要係個腦入邊 由中文轉英文講既話<br />\n我都覺得你唔好去做算啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:07:18.000Z","msg":"坦白講樓主 <br />\n我有個朋友都好似你咁 但最後都係因為英文放棄左<br />\n而最重要既野係佢都係讀到大學先<br />\n「突然之間想做」呢個先係致命既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你既對手有兩種 1.從小想做+英文好 2.英文好<br />\n你既熱誠同英文都唔夠人黎 好難捱到最後架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我講呢番說話係唔想你最後覺得浪費時間唔開心<br />\n但你如果想堅持既話 一定要加油！"},{"pid":"83f6d28d207f0a05f8930936f790ac11de750945","tid":794700,"uid":181853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb09b5b5a4958f7e36342dae82550ee77344767f","tid":794700,"uid":24764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"真係識人考到 但條友本身英文好撚勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"都係英文要好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eceb73b229a6852c961df5db961a2cd1a44d7790","tid":794700,"uid":181853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7234ceaeb86c11c7bad9cc3cdad4c52d78a5de65","tid":794700,"uid":197852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"唔好害人啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"我都係問下啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea87e6143d24ff9fc219a35d777b0d7c97b3885","tid":794700,"uid":181853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a07447409b4c98bde45e5a17637195f3bfdca96","tid":794700,"uid":36296,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"Eng level3 <br />\n唔係話